## Ventures (pre-commitment)

```dataview
TABLE
  stage,
  revisit_after as "Revisit",
  updated
FROM "wiki/ventures"
WHERE stage != "committed" AND stage != "killed"
SORT updated DESC
```

**Ventures overdue for commit/kill decision** (12+ months old, still undecided):

```dataview
TABLE
  stage,
  created as "Started thinking"
FROM "wiki/ventures"
WHERE created < date(today) - dur(365 days)
AND stage != "committed" AND stage != "killed"
SORT created ASC
```

