## Recent activity

**Summaries ingested in the last 14 days:**

```dataview
TABLE
  source_type,
  source_date as "Source date",
  created as "Ingested"
FROM "wiki/summaries"
WHERE created >= date(today) - dur(14 days)
SORT created DESC
```

**Any wiki page updated in the last 7 days:**

```dataview
LIST "(" + kind + ") " + title
FROM "wiki"
WHERE updated >= date(today) - dur(7 days)
AND !contains(file.path, "index.md")
AND !contains(file.path, "log.md")
AND !contains(file.path, "RESOLVER.md")
AND !contains(file.name, "README")
SORT updated DESC
```

