## Stale alert

**Active projects with no update in 30 days:**

```dataview
TABLE
  business,
  updated as "Last update"
FROM "wiki/projects"
WHERE status = "active"
AND updated < date(today) - dur(30 days)
SORT updated ASC
```

Active + no recent activity = drift. Change `status` to `paused` or
`shipped`, or actually work on it.

**Decisions 90+ days old worth revisiting:**

```dataview
TABLE
  business,
  date
FROM "wiki/decisions"
WHERE status = "accepted"
AND date < date(today) - dur(90 days)
SORT date ASC
LIMIT 10
```

