## Adding your own queries

Dataview syntax: https://blacksmithgu.github.io/obsidian-dataview/

Common patterns:

- `TABLE field1, field2 FROM "folder" WHERE condition` — tables
- `LIST FROM "folder"` — just the file links
- `WHERE business = "slug"` — filter by parent business
- `WHERE cluster = "work"` — filter themes by cluster
- `WHERE created >= date(today) - dur(30 days)` — time filter
- `SORT field DESC` — ordering

The agent can write queries for you — just ask. Every page it creates
carries the frontmatter these queries need.
